  tactical decision (the same gesture Red Mag uses, 
  picked up consciously over twenty years of mentorship); 
  switches into Welsh under stress; takes notes in a 
  small spiral-bound notebook in pencil
- Coterie role: Red Mag's chief tactical officer; the 
  lieutenant who plans operations; the closest to Red Mag 
  personally; manages the Footscray contingency-card 
  network's day-to-day
- Binding: Red Mag rescued her from Final Death in 2003 
